quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  4,60,"Day ur twalav ara wid iumnen, zi$emma, s wayen ik ed irsen, d wayen id irsen, uqbel ik? B$an aêuddu iôebbiten n tkerkas, ulamma pwamôen a ten nekôen. Ib$a Cciîan a ten itlef ttelfan u$miq"
  4,61,"Ma nnan asen: \"aset ed ar wayen id Issers Öebbi, akw ar Umazan\", a pwaliv ixabiten wexxôen ak, ugin"
  4,62,"Amek ihi, ma u$en tiyta, ilmend n wayen xedmen ifassen nnsen, sinna, a d asen $uôek, ad ggalen s Öebbi: \"neb$a kan lewqama akked lembwafqa"
  4,63,"Widak, Iéôa Öebbi i illan deg ulawen nnsen. Ihi, îîixeô asen, nabi iten, meslay iten, $ef iman nnsen, s wawal iqenâen"
  4,64,"Ur d Nuzen Amazan, siwa kan iwakken ad as a$en awal, ma Irad Öebbi. Wid idensen iman nnsen, ma usan k id, d$a ssutren ssmaê i Öebbi, u issuter Umazan ad ppusemmêen, ad afen Öebbi Issuruf, Ipêunu"
  4,65,"Xaîi! S Mass ik, ur ppamnen, alamma rran k d amêaddi, deg wayen i$ef mgarraden. Sinna, ur ppafen, deg iman nnsen, ara ten ihewwlen, deg wayen id têuddev. Ad anzen yal annuz"
  4,66,"Lemmer i sen Nuri: \"mmin$et\"! Ne$ \"ff$et seg ixxamen nnwen\"! Ur p xeddmen, siwa kra segsen. Ppif, i nitni, lemmer xdimen ayen u$uô pwanecden. D atebbet uûwib"
  4,67,"Imiren ad asen Nefk, s$uône£, arraz ameqwôaêan"
  4,68,A ten Nenhu s abrid uwqim
  4,69,"Wid ippa$en awal i Öebbi akked Umazan, widak atnan ar wid I$at Öebbi ger lambiyya, wid issdaqen, ccuhada, ûûalêin. Ay telha tdukli d wigi"
  4,70,Wagi d lfevl s$uô Öebbi. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Amusnaw